    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心打造你的鬼屋，让游客们心惊胆战，毛骨悚然。设计和定制每个魔鬼细节，让你的游客们心惊肉跳，在到达出口之前，让他们魂不附体，不然你就要冒着失去恐怖声誉和金钱的风险。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >建造</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造墙、门、活板门、假墙等陷阱，在游客们穿越恐怖迷宫时引导并迷惑他们，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你急于建造或想要尝试不同的风格，你可以使用预先造好的走廊和房间。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f8c08d0744ebc44478232f0a8df7a4f3.poster.avif?t=1751322573\" width=480 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f8c08d0744ebc44478232f0a8df7a4f3.webm?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f8c08d0744ebc44478232f0a8df7a4f3.mp4?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >定制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用灯光效果、幽灵图画、鬼怪道具等装扮你的景点。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最能惊吓游客的颜色。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/b8652de8962ad936eb32b6f5af321a4b.poster.avif?t=1751322573\" width=480 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/b8652de8962ad936eb32b6f5af321a4b.webm?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/b8652de8962ad936eb32b6f5af321a4b.mp4?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >惊恐</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >沿途设置恐怖陷阱，包括鬼怪和外星人等所有恐怖元素。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买具有恐怖声誉的新景点，但你要小心，拥有相同的景点越多，且它们彼此越近，则可能会让你的游客失去恐惧感。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f1c66c52021473fe421393ba7501e2b2.poster.avif?t=1751322573\" width=480 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f1c66c52021473fe421393ba7501e2b2.webm?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/f1c66c52021473fe421393ba7501e2b2.mp4?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精心准备</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确保你的景点已准备好迎接下一波游客，让我们拭目以待。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着每波访客的增加，利润滚滚而来，你的恐怖声誉也在不断增加。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过游客们戴在脖子上的荧光棒，可以查看他们的忍受限度。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >变得狡诈难测</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你越进步，就越更需要努力惊吓你的客人们。险恶的陷阱确实可以是场噩梦，因为你可以让客人们从生者环境中消失，让他们加入死者行列。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不要被抓住，否则你的生涯就此结束。一定要聘请你能负担得起的最好的保安和律师，让调查远离你。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/7bdbaedbd25059170fb404b1c6f59d91.poster.avif?t=1751322573\" width=480 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/7bdbaedbd25059170fb404b1c6f59d91.webm?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1506680/extras/7bdbaedbd25059170fb404b1c6f59d91.mp4?t=1751322573\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>一旦你赢得了足够的恐怖声誉，你将能够进入下一步，搬迁到新的地方，在城镇的不同地方迎接新的挑战。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进展</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不同地点有：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鬼魅后院</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >森林</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >老工厂</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废弃的校舍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >马戏团</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废弃的医院</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废弃的商业广场</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >废弃的游乐园</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以及更多有趣的场所！</p></li></ul>",
